general.name: sdR
general.description: This file contains raw spectro data from the BOSS/eBOSS/BHM spectro CCDs. Simultaneous frames in different chips all have the same frame number. Which frames are what type of observation is indicated by the FLAVOR keyword in each header. HDU 0 contains the raw counts as integers (4352x4224). For SDSS-I raw spectro data, please look at SDSS-I,-II sdR files:https://data.sdss.org/datamodel/files/RAWDATA_DIR/MJD/sdR.html.

surveys.name: eBOSS
surveys.description: A cosmological survey of quasars and galaxies to understand baryon acoustic oscillations

releases.name: DR18
releases.description: SDSS unreleased data.  Represents any work-in-progress data.

general.naming_convention: sdR-[br][12]-[FRAME].fit, indicating which blue or red spectrograph (1 or 2), and the frame number.

changelog.description: Describes changes to the datamodel product and/or file structure from one release to another
